{"tid":1982111,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做了這件事可以令你不用怕經濟蕭條","createTime":"2020-04-21T04:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T08:02:49.000Z","uid":184558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2edbd356e57181b62f6bb0598caa4fd312d9a64","tid":1982111,"uid":184558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"[睇之前幫手推and簽]<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f3e66d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n<br />\n係武漢肺炎下全世界停工停市<br />\n經濟衰退已經提早出現<br />\n香港有好多企業都捱唔住要執<br />\n可以預見肺炎之後會有一堆紅色資本進駐香港<br />\n<br />\n而全世界(e.g. 美國 英國 其他陸續有嚟)都會趁呢個機會叫中國賠錢同撤資<br />\n中國一旦真係要賠錢/失去外資香港都唇亡齒寒<br />\n香港一嚟會不斷比各種大白象紅色資本中出<br />\n二嚟各行各業都會大受打擊<br />\n<br />\n除非話比人聽香港都係受害者<br />\n叫人幫我地攞番我地呢幾個月冇左嘅錢<br />\n同比人知道呢單野唔關香港事<br />\n冇錯就係叫美國幫手<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f3e66d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n聯署要求美國協助香港追討損失<br />\n全世界排華風氣已經形成<br />\n呢個時候要做嘅係企係西方國家個邊<br />\n如果唔係大灣區等緊大家<br />\n我地而家要做嘅係話比美國聽香港撐你所以你搞中國唔好搞我地<br />\n同比佢知我地想佢點幫我地<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f3e66d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a><br />\n而家要多六萬三千人簽<br />\n每人簽完揾多兩個人簽好快就搞掂<br />\n香港會變大灣區定有望獨立就睇大家了<br />\n<br />\n無成本簽個名唔係唔做啊<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frequest-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiUPYNnpCCLo8Mp68exG%2FaA0%3D&h=f3e66d4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/request-reparation-behalf-hong-kong-people-loss-due-chinese-virus</a>"},{"pid":"b9ae4acaaa752b7cb04bf7a2b7285e3898a937e4","tid":1982111,"uid":174060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T08:02:49.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}